\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Originally I had a clear idea that was inspired by an example soundscape that was used for an earlier discussion post. \'93 Imagine This: A Story Told with Sound Effect\'94 is a soundscape that only uses sound effects to tell a story that has a twist at the end. I wanted to take this idea and morph it to my life. My first two rough drafts were just sound effects that walked you through a day in the life but I wasn't satisfied with the final project. I decided to tweak my project and change the theme to the repetitive nature of a student's everyday life.\'a0
