\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 My soundscape starts with an average day in the life. I used about 12 different sound effects to mimic everyday sounds such as an alarm clock, shower, walking on pavement, etc. After the first set of sound effects play through it repeats itself but, this time the sounds are a little shorter, speeding up the day. The final run through is even shorter than the second one which reminds me of scenes in movies when time is passing and the clock is running very quickly while the character is completing the task. It is so easy to get caught up in a routine when there is so much on a student's plate.\'a0
